### 7. UI COMPONENTS & CSS CLASSES

**StatusBadge:**
- Inline span with uppercase text
- Border matches status color
- Colors: active, resolved, closed, draft

**ProbabilityBar:**
- Horizontal bar with colored segments per outcome
- Colors (cycling): green, red, blue, yellow, purple, pink, teal, orange
- Legend below with outcome names and probabilities

**CSS Variables (from theme):**
- `--color-primary` - Primary action color
- `--color-success` - Green success (#22c55e)
- `--color-danger` - Red danger (#ef4444)
- `--color-warning` - Orange warning
- `--color-bg` - Background
- `--color-bg-surface` - Surface background
- `--color-bg-hover` - Hover background
- `--color-text` - Primary text
- `--color-text-muted` - Muted text
- `--color-border` - Border color
- `--radius-sm` - Small border radius
- `--radius-md` - Medium border radius
- `--space-xs`, `--space-sm`, `--space-md`, `--space-lg`, `--space-xl` - Spacing
- `--font-mono` - Monospace font

---

### 8. QUERY HOOKS (Data Management)

**File:** `/tmp/temporal-worktrees/task-e2e-tests-001/frontend/src/lib/query/hooks.ts`

**Query Keys Pattern:**
```typescript
queryKeys = {
  markets: (filters?) => ["markets", normalized_filters],
  market: (id) => ["markets", id],
  marketEvents: (id) => ["markets", id, "events"],
  marketComments: (id) => ["markets", id, "comments"],
  engineStats: (id) => ["markets", id, "engine-stats"],
  marketAnalytics: (id, interval?) => ["markets", id, "analytics", interval],
  accountRisk: (id) => ["accounts", id, "risk"],
  accountExposure: (id) => ["accounts", id, "exposure"],
  marketPnl: (marketId, accountId) => ["markets", marketId, "accounts", accountId, "pnl"],
  accountPnl: (accountId) => ["accounts", accountId, "pnl"],
}
```

**Refetch Intervals:**
- Markets: 5000ms
- Market detail: 5000ms
- Market analytics: 30000ms
- Account P&L: 30000ms

**WebSocket Subscriptions:**
- `useMarketPriceSubscription(marketId)` - Updates marginals in real-time
- `useMarketEventSubscription(marketId)` - Invalidates events query
- `useAccountRiskSubscription(accountId)` - Updates risk/exposure

---

### 9. FORMAT UTILITIES

**File:** `/tmp/temporal-worktrees/task-e2e-tests-001/frontend/src/lib/utils/format.ts`

```typescript
formatProbability(p: number): string  // "45.3%"
formatCurrency(n: number): string     // "1.2M", "45.3K", or "123.45"
truncateHash(hash: string): string    // "sha256:a1b2c3d8…" or "abcd1234…"
formatRelativeTime(iso: string): string  // "3m ago", "2h ago", "1d ago", "just now"
timeUntil(iso: string): string        // "5d 3h", "23h 45m", or "expired"
statusColor(status: string): string   // CSS color variable for status
```

---

### 10. ERROR HANDLING

**BayesApiError Exception:**
```typescript
class BayesApiError extends Error {
  status: number;
  code: string;
  details: Record<string, unknown>;
}
```

**Common Error Codes:**
- `account_not_found` (status 404)
- `position_limit_exceeded` - Includes requestedSize, currentNetSize, resultingNetSize, maxPositionSize details
- `no_orders_found` (status 404)

---

### 11. FORM PAYLOADS FOR API SUBMISSIONS

**Create Market:**
```typescript
{
  title: string;
  description: string;
  outcomes: Array<{ id: string; name: string }>;
  expires_at: string;  // ISO datetime
  liquidity?: number;
}
```

**Event Trade:**
```typescript
{
  accountId: string;
  formula: Array<Array<{ variableId: string; outcomeId: string; negated: boolean }>>;
  size: number;
  side: "buy" | "sell";
  idempotencyKey?: string;
}
```

**Market Comment:**
```typescript
{
  accountId: string;
  body: string;
  idempotencyKey?: string;
}
```

**Resolve Market:**
```typescript
{
  accountId: string;
  outcomeId?: string;
  finalProbabilities?: Record<string, number>;
  idempotencyKey?: string;
}
```

